parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag light comes on intermittently
the airbag system fails to deploy in a crash
the SRS light is on
the airbag system is malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to control, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn
the steering wheel vibrates or shakes
the vehicle pulls to one side
the power steering pump fails
the steering rack leaks fluid
and the steering shaft binds or twists.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag dashboard light flickers or stays on
the passenger airbag light flashes on and off
and the airbag system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, potentially leading to fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates without warning
the accelerator pedal sticks
the brakes do not respond or are difficult to apply
the vehicle surges forward
and the engine RPM increases rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, potentially leading to fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes do not respond or are difficult to apply
the vehicle does not slow down or stop as expected
and the brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause unintended acceleration, loss of control, accidents, and injuries, potentially leading to fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control system does not disengage when the brake pedal is pressed
the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly
and the accelerator pedal sticks.
